<p><a name="1980s" id="1980s"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Stuart_Hall_(cultural_theorist)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: 1980s">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">1980s</span></h3>
<ul>
